race.comment: JOHN DORY (1) saluted over this distance range at Canterbury at the latest effort and looks to have plenty of upside. Further improvement in store and has to be considered carefully. KRUMAC (14) has placed over this course and distance and gets in on the minimum weight. Top-three aspirations. POWER REECE (5) has put back-to-back wins together and Thompson sticks in the saddle. Should give backers a sight. SHORTCUT (9) next best from the inside marble.
